    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>⚠️ 请注意：</strong></i><br><i>《Blue Maiden》是一款节奏缓慢的步行模拟游戏，专注于氛围、探索和解谜。这不是一款<strong>动作导向的恐怖游戏</strong>，也<strong>不包含</strong>战斗或快节奏玩法。如果你想要肾上腺素飙升的恐怖体验，这可能并不适合你。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧩 关于本作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/9f800d28198226582b53496bace809e5.poster.avif?t=1768949653\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/9f800d28198226582b53496bace809e5.webm?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/9f800d28198226582b53496bace809e5.mp4?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Blue Maiden</i> 是一款日本第一人称心理恐怖游戏，恐怖感会缓慢而细致地渗透进来。你扮演刚从大学毕业的橘太一，回到童年生活的街区帮忙家族生意——却发现街道异常空荡，空气中弥漫着恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你总是被同一个梦魇缠绕：一个神秘的女孩静静地站在樱花树下。但当梦境开始侵入现实生活时，你意识到出了大问题。踏入这个逐渐衰败的城镇，揭开<strong>Blue Maiden</strong>传说背后的真相。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔍 主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围探索：</strong><br>慢慢探索日本传统的诡异场景，配合沉浸式音效与视觉表现。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖：</strong><br>通过故事和环境营造不安氛围，以轻微惊吓和令人不适的画面引发内心恐惧，而非突然吓人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/c2e477153d5ccc9775246d63f3251e0f.poster.avif?t=1768949653\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/c2e477153d5ccc9775246d63f3251e0f.webm?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/c2e477153d5ccc9775246d63f3251e0f.mp4?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>环境叙事：</strong><br>寻找线索，解开环境谜题，通过细腻的叙述拼凑出Blue Maiden的真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局：</strong><br>完整通关约需1小时，寻找全部3个结局的玩家可体验额外约30分钟内容。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实日式场景：</strong><br>灵感来源于经典日式恐怖，《Blue Maiden》融合了民间传说、忧郁和神秘，带来独特的惊悚体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/f6ec105dd37fd58fe7dfc283726e4eea.poster.avif?t=1768949653\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/f6ec105dd37fd58fe7dfc283726e4eea.webm?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391690/extras/f6ec105dd37fd58fe7dfc283726e4eea.mp4?t=1768949653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👁️ 你能揭开Blue Maiden背后的真相吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻声前行，仔细观察。并不是一切都愿意被发现。</p>",
